events.description: The next talk.js will be on Wednesday June 17th. Important: the meetup location has moved temporarily to PayPal Singapore. Scheduled Talks: • Web components build stacks - Sebastiaan Deckers • 10 to 100+ local player games with HappyFunTimes - Gregg Tavares • How to kickstartVR Website - Tee Jia Hen Leave a comment if you want to give a talk! Location: PayPal Singapore Suntec Tower 5 5 Temasek Boulevard #09-01 Singapore 038985 Remember to bring photo ID to get through building security. Feel free to ask questions in the SingaporeJS gitter room: https://gitter.im/SingaporeJS/discussions See you there!
